### Delivery Controller Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = PUT_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@driverToken = PUT_DRIVER_TOKEN_HERE
@customerToken = PUT_CUSTOMER_TOKEN_HERE
@deliveryId = PUT_DELIVERY_ID_HERE
@orderId = PUT_ORDER_ID_HERE
@fileId = PUT_FILE_ID_HERE


### ─── الأدمن ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Admin: Create Internal Delivery (إنشاء توصيل داخلي)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "type": "INTERNAL",
  "driverId": "PUT_DRIVER_UUID_HERE",
  "estimatedAt": "2026-06-07T10:00:00.000Z",
  "notes": "توصيل سريع"
}


### Admin: Create External Delivery (توصيل خارجي)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "type": "EXTERNAL",
  "courierName": "DHL",
  "trackingNumber": "DHL-123456789",
  "trackingUrl": "https://dhl.com/track/123456789"
}


### Admin: Get All Deliveries (كل التوصيلات)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Admin: Filter Deliveries by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries?status=ASSIGNED
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Admin: Filter Deliveries by Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries?type=INTERNAL
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Admin: Filter Deliveries by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries?dateFrom=2026-01-01&dateTo=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Admin: Get Delivery Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Admin: Update Delivery (Change Driver, Tracking, etc.)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "تحديث الملاحظات",
  "estimatedAt": "2026-06-08T14:00:00.000Z"
}


### Admin: Update Delivery Status → OUT_FOR_DELIVERY
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "OUT_FOR_DELIVERY"
}


### Admin: Update Delivery Status → DELIVERED (يُحدّث الطلب تلقائياً)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "DELIVERED",
  "note": "تم التوصيل بنجاح"
}


### ─── السائق ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Driver: Get My Deliveries (توصيلاتي)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/my
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Driver: Filter My Deliveries by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/my?status=ASSIGNED
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Driver: Update Status → PICKED_UP
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PICKED_UP"
}


### Driver: Update Status → OUT_FOR_DELIVERY
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "OUT_FOR_DELIVERY"
}


### Driver: Upload Proof Image (رفع صورة إثبات)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}/proof
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fileId": "{{fileId}}",
  "recipientName": "أحمد محمد"
}


### ─── أخطاء ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Delivery Already Exists (توصيل مكرر)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "type": "INTERNAL",
  "driverId": "PUT_DRIVER_UUID_HERE"
}


### Invalid Status Transition (نقل حالة غير صالح)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "DELIVERED"
}


### Driver: Access Not Assigned Delivery (توصيل ليس لك)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PICKED_UP"
}


### Proof in Wrong Status (حالة غير مناسبة للإثبات)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}/proof
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fileId": "{{fileId}}"
}


### Missing Driver for Internal Delivery
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "type": "INTERNAL"
}


### Missing Courier Name for External Delivery
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "type": "EXTERNAL"
}


### Unauthorized (بدون توكن)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries
Accept-Language: ar


### Customer Accessing Admin Route (ممنوع)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/deliveries
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Admin Accessing Driver Route (ممنوع)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/my
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
